msgid "Scenario III: Return to The Secret Name"
msgstr "冒险III：重返隐密之名"

msgid "Add the 4 new \"Unknown Places\" locations to the original 7."
msgstr "将4张新的未知地点卡牌加入7张原版未知地点卡牌中。"

msgid "Set the Witch House Ruins aside and randomly remove 4 Unknown Places locations from the game."
msgstr "将屋宅遗址放在一边，并随机将4张未知地点卡牌从游戏中移除。"

msgid "As part of the tarot campaign reading you performed, place \"The Hermit · IX\" in the reversed position."
msgstr "你的塔罗剧本解牌是逆位的“隐士·IX”。"

msgid "As part of the tarot campaign reading you performed, place \"The Hermit · IX\" in the upright position."
msgstr "你的塔罗剧本解牌是正位的“隐士·IX”。"
